{
  "arquivo": "ca06_04",
  "total": 46,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(I think the meeting place was around here.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(It's still a bit early...\\n but there's not enough time to look around\\n other places. I'll just wait for them.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "???",
      "texto_en": "Futaro-kun? Why are you looking around so much?\\nIt's dangerous if you don't watch where you're going,\\nyou know?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...Eh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Hi, there!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Oh, it's Ichika.\\nYou're already here.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, I wanted to take a break and rest here.\\nI walked around so much that I got thirsty.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What's that?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "It's a frozen drink made with 'shikuwasa' citrus fruit.\\nIt's exclusive to Okinawa, so I was curious about it.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "You're dressed up in glasses and everything\\njust for juice on the go.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Well, I AM an actress, after all.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "But, I guess I can take them off.\\n...Since I'm glad you came, Futaro-kun.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I didn't come just for you.\\nThis is the meeting place.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "I know that much.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Are you alone?\\nThe others aren't with you?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, I wanted to be with just you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "!...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "So, it wasn't a coincidence.\\nI was waiting for you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Wha?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "By the way, Futaro-kun,\\nyou're still unable to drink coffee, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Huh? Ahh, well, no.\\nIt's all bitter.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Ahaha, you still haven't grown.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "But, more importantly, what are you planning?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "What do you mean?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Well... Wanting to see places together with me,\\nwaiting for me here.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "You know. You don't have to ask. Right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I mean, I don't...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Even though you're still unable to drink coffee%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "This is what I'm thinking you should do.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Huh?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Here, why don't you try drinking this, Futaro-kun?\\nIt's sweet and sour, so it might be refreshing.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "No, wait a minute.\\nThat sounds gross.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "It's not bad at all. It's quite delicious,\\nand livens you up.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "That's not what I meant...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "So, what did you mean?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "???",
      "texto_en": "Ichika?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Oh no, too bad.\\nTime's up.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Hmm, that's what's going on.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "E-excuse us.\\nIt seems we had bad timing...didn't we?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Itsuki",
      "texto_en": "Yotsuba.\\nYou don't have to worry about it.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "No, it's not like that%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Nino",
      "texto_en": "Fu-kun, we want to do some secret shopping,\\njust the two of us, so please wait here.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...Right.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Okay, see you sooon.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(I hope nothing weird happens.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}